{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, there were 20 or so of us, and I think we were dispersed in two or three homes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We spent a night there to, to relax and gather our strength.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we were greeted by a French passeur, who told us what our next step would be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The next step was to cross the frontier between occupied France and unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was called the [NON-ENGLISH], the demarcation line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were told that we would be taking a train to Navarre because there were no customs or no problem within occupied France up to Navarre.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Navarre was in the frontier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There, we would be met by, again, other people who would tell us what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We did this, and we got to Navarre quite late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I somehow have a blank there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I can't remember what we did for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I knew that we were told we would be crossing the frontier at daybreak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we would be walking for about two or three hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we would have to do this in compete silence because there were Germans and German dogs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But if we followed them very silently and not too near-- I remember we sort of-- we more or less walked in a line.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And although it was October, the weather wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We duly did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We heard, heard the German dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I suppose we were just numb at that, at that stage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We just-- we never discussed our fear, our anguish, our hopes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We just did what we wanted to do and we were told.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And after about three hours, we arrived in unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
